Collection of Information



This proposed rule would not increase the paperwork burden on the public. The only paperwork involves ship design
calculations used in the development of stability information, but this information is already subject to review
by the Coast Guard under 46 CFR 170.110. The Coast Guard previously submitted the requirements regarding its collection
