(5) Roads leading into waste dump areas and tailing areas from inhabited or public areas are required to be blocked
off and warning signs posted on the perimeter of such areas. A.R.S. Section 27-317.

(6) The primary responsibility for the control and abatement of air pollution rests with the Arizona Department of
